text: Kenyan Catholic doctors reject the Covid-19 vaccine calling it unsafe and unnecessary
The Covid-19 vaccines are not safe because people are dying and getting seriously ill as a result of receiving them.
Eight reasons not to get vaccinated against Covid-19
People not vaccinated against COVID-19 came out the best.
The vaccines won’t stop me getting Covid-19.

People who were undergoing chemotherapy have been told that they should not receive vaccines, and should stay away from people who had received vaccines, and now because of Covid-19 this has all changed.
Vaccines don’t stop you getting Covid-19 or spreading it.
Young, healthy people don't need to worry about getting the COVID-19 vaccine.
